1. Summary: Bug1: Field E-mail: Local part accepts more than 64 characters.
Severity: Average.
Steps:
1. go to https://en.belavia.by/leader/registration/
2. Contact Information, field E-mail.
3. Input Local part more than 64 characters.

Actual result: Local part accepts more than 64 characters.
Expected result: the field is highlighted in red (according to a list of valid and invalid examples of emails, according to RFC 2822).
Attachements: screenshot: https://github.com/Volha2407/Defects/blob/main/Bug1.png
Environment: Windows 10 32-bit Chrome 90.0



1. Summary: Bug2: Field Пасажыры: displays incorrect word form while choosing 3 passengers.
Severity: Minor.
Steps:
1. Go to https://dc-booking.belavia.by/
2. Tab Пошук, field Пасажыры.
3. In the drop-down list choose Дарослы and other passengers to make 3 passengers at all.

Actual result: the field Пасажыры displays 3 Пасажыра.
Expected result: the field Пасажыры displays 3 Пасажыры.

note:
When selecting 4 passengers, the same error occurs.

Attachements: screenshot: https://github.com/Volha2407/Defects/blob/main/Bug2.png
Environment: Windows 10 32-bit Chrome 90.0
